Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Hebat sekali, kau bisa bicara.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sepertinya jika tidak menghancurkan makhluk ini,{\b0}
